{"title":"长跑之歌","authors":["韩笑"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":4,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长跑之歌韩笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你锻炼身体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么要跑一万米？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我敞开肺腑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱这广阔天地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——在班房里放风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只准走十米。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今怎能不珍惜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长跑的权利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你年过半百"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必同小伙子比？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不争名次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争的是志气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——笑看年轻人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷超过去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我暗自庆幸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春和我在一起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一身是病"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么能坚持到底？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了亲人和敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要冲刺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——向阴风和冷雨示威，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对星星和月亮宣誓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病夫犹在征途跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华儿女不可欺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你喜气洋溢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎有什么秘密？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在长跑中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发现了诗情画意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——信不信由你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不妨试试。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑一万米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追一万行诗！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}